gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Knicks 109, Rockets 94
gameRecap.excerpt: The Knicks defeated the Rockets, 109-94. Julius Randle (31 points, eight rebounds, four assists, four 3PM) and Jalen Brunson (30 points, seven assists, four 3PM) combined for 61 points for the Knicks in the victory, while Fred VanVleet tallied 24 points, 12 assists and five 3PM for the Rockets in the losing effort. The Knicks improve to 24-17 on the season, while the Rockets fall to 19-21.
